cross: Sarcochilus Rosella x Sarcochilus Kulnura Sweetie

measurements.description: Forty-three flowers and 55 buds on eight up to 24-cm upright or slightly arching inflorescences; sepals and petals white, blotched and spotted pink, barred dark red basally, spotted red centrally on reverse; lip white, blotched yellow, saccate; substance firm; texture crystalline.
